3 > 2 → rejected.

Hmm. Let's recalculate. n=6, √6=2.45, 6/2.45=2.45, max(2, 2.45)=2.
So max_coverage rounds to 2.

Persistent asthma covers 3 → exceeds 2 → rejected as a grouper.

